# MyBuddy – AI-Powered Digital Productivity Companion

## 🌐 Project Overview

**MyBuddy** is a no-code digital companion designed to help users manage tasks, notes, and routines efficiently. Built using no-code AI tools, it serves as a productivity hub for time-conscious individuals.


https://mybuddy.lovable.app/

## 🛠️ Tools & Technologies Used
- No-code Builder: Lovable
- Workflow Logic: Zapier (automation)
- AI: Prompt Engineering (OpenAI)
- Branding & UI Design

## 💡 Features
- Task manager with reminders
- Daily note-taking
- Quick access to web utilities
- User-friendly and responsive UI

## 🎯 Business Value
Designed for productivity-focused individuals, freelancers, and students who need a central hub for managing daily tasks.

